Word clock is inspired by

  http://www.qlocktwo.com/info.php?lang=en

and

  http://blog.makezine.com/archive/2009/09/qlocktwo_clock_tells_time_with_word.html

I don't recall now where I first encountered it. Someone's link on Twitter.

Change history:

* 2.0.x: Improved "app" functionality, improved settings UI, code cleanup.
* 2.1.x: Added support for specifying a time zone. More code cleanup.
